Hello- working on a coded blog index file that is a variation on the "Barricade" template. This template has a hero image background that I'm trying to change-  is this a user setting, if not where I am I missing it in the code? Here is the relevant code section (I think) {% extends "./layouts/base.html" %}

{% block body %}
&lt;div class="blog-hero"&gt;
  &lt;h1 class="blog-hero__title"&gt;{{ group.public_title }}&lt;/h1&gt;
  &lt;h4 class="blog-header__subtitle"&gt;{{ group.description }}&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
